CustomField.description: Defines the estimated WorkCover amount per unit that will be applied to the Superannuation for the Pay Rate
CustomField.formula: If ( OR( RecordType.DeveloperName = "Payment", RecordType.DeveloperName = "Allowance" ), If( OR( tc9_pr__WorkCover_Exempt__c, tc9_pr__Contributes_to_OTE__c = FALSE ), 0, tc9_pr__Assignment_Rate__r.tc9_pr__Estimated_WorkCover_on_Super__c * tc9_pr__Pay_Multiplier__c ), 0 )
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines the estimated WorkCover amount per unit that will be applied to the Superannuation for the Pay Rate
CustomField.label: Estimated WorkCover on Super Unit
